one thing I will say, im genuinely jealous of Europeans and people from like Australia trying to cold approach because (even just in the backdrop of your conversations), most of the women out and about are decently attractive and a lot are very attractive... here in the US, we have normalized sloth like behavior, so much so, that when trying to approach a woman, you will have 20 walk by, 10 will be visually overweight/obese, another 5 are lesbians/shaved heads, and of the remaining 5, only 1 will be single.. not saying it's impossible, just that we have truly shot ourselves in the foot with this numbers game the last 20 or so years... may be time to break out the passport and put some skills to work..
